    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the road in this wonderful find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a dependable and smooth driving experience you can count on. It\u2019s a solid, high-quality choice that\u2019s ready for its next adventure!",
